    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Other commercial hood brands we service</h2>
      <p>
        CaptiveAire is market leader, but we service the rest of the commercial hood manufacturers LA restaurants run, each
        with its own quirks:
      </p>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/halton-hood-repair/">Halton hood repair</a>, Finnish family, Capture Jet + UV-Hood + MARVEL DCV; LA Michelin and 5-star hotel install base</li>
